text: <@U31A496G2> not sure i’m following the 2nd part of your question, but in general generating unique ids from inside the chaincode would involve some kind of random number engine and it’s not a good idea to do that, as it makes the chaincode non-deterministic. it’s best to generate this value from the application and pass it in. again not understanding your 2nd part of the question so not sure if i’m answering the right question :wink:
